metadata.name: PROTECT BLACK TRANS LIVES (2020)
metadata.description:
Title: PROTECT BLACK TRANS LIVES (2020)  
Date Photographed: June 10th, 2020  
Location: Downtown Los Angeles, California, USA 
Photographer: Raven Trammell

We had been marching for a few miles at this point. We stopped to gather for a moment, as the organizers of the march motivated us through their bull horns. 

"WE NEED EACH OTHER MORE THAN EVER!" 

This was moments before LAPD shut down all public transportation. Leaving hundreds of protestors stranded. Rather than panic, we continued our march in the streets of Downtown Los Angeles.
